name: #2 POSTCAD FROM BARCELONA (back)
description:
I have been a long time thinking about my fate and I only gave the possibility to be what I choose for me, maybe that one was my fate.
 
I have been a rebel traveler for years, wanting so much freedom that one day it became condemnation. I just wanted to go away to see the world. 

I saw it.
But, by the way, today I think more about what I do.
To be a youth traveler going around was great, being an adult creating my life is something to think about seriously.

Today I´m happy about what I did. Sometimes I just want to come back to old times, but I know like the day I wrote this: 

"We are our movement"
So we have to continue the road,
but today is no longer being alone for me.
